Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Set sail for Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Solitary Island in the Distant Sea!\NThe Legendary Lost Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contacting all squad captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble on the deck of Ship #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the resource manager?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Turn the yard this way!\N--No, no! To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get repair planks\Nfrom the other ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repair Team!\NGet to work repairing Ship #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quicker at running\Nthan I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries. It'd be best to\Nlet them go for now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went to such dangerous lengths\Nto escape from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten\Nthis island has a legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story about the dragons'\Nnest on Lost Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you saying they...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if so, they'll wind up\Nbeing the perfect guides there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting to Commodore Nelson?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragonite I seek...\NThe elixir of immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd ever hand it over\Nto the likes of Nelson Royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a flawless\NEric the Whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore, sir! Please have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Commodore Nelson Royal!\N--Oh! It's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a report from Eric, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's a message from a soldier\Nworking at Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eric has located the\Nlegendary Millennial Dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He goes on to say that all ships\Nare presently busy repairing damage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the flagship received.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Eric...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why've you not reported to me\Nafter finding the Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to take the\NDragonite all for yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing more than a hired soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main forces will now\Nhead for Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Island, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The map doesn't have any islands\Nin the waters around Warship Island
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that fit the bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Grandpa Ryu!\NWhich way should we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he went to sleep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she cook again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was waiting for her food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made today's meal--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat lots, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. I made all that food\Nand it goes to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just make some more, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point is we shouldn't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragons' nest...\NIt's east of Warship Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's where Lost Island is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said he just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know where!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Island is east of Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Take the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's rush\Nstraight for Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You better eat all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've changed course?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! The pirate ship appears\Nto be headed for the waters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,east of Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're making their move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the bows eastward!\NFull speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now going to close\Nin on the Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannoneers to the gun batteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, prepare for Level 3 combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Lost Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here, Zoro.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you go, Zoro.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here, Zoro.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hand 'em\Nto me without talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Island is at the\Nend of this great ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of island could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! See anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we've come a long way, but\Nthere's no sign of an island at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd remember\Nsome more details or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bonk Grandpa Ryu\Nin the head with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think maybe then the shock'll\Nhelp him remember something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:10:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Grandpa Ryu! We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's there, right? The dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you go to the dragons' nest,\Nyou'll get better, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so goofy, thanking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not even there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They followed us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well! We'll see when we get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! I don't think\Nyou're troubling me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It turned into an argument at some point.\N--Hey! Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It turned into an argument at some point.\N--Hey! Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It looks more like Apis is\N--Hey! Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It looks more like Apis is\N--Pretending to sleep isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the only one who's angry, though...\N--Pretending to sleep isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the only one who's angry, though...\N--Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you think we should stop her?\N--Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something's definitely\Nnot right about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Nami! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The pirate ship!\N--This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What just happened?!\NWhy did they disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All ships, full stop!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone to wait on\Nstandby until my next orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! There's no\Ntelling what's in the waters ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have them prepare a small craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seriously going to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm going on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Nami was in\Nbig trouble again or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our own ship was right in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we went right through it... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost like... a mirage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirage? That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read about this a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said temperature differences\Nbetween warm and cold ocean water
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can create mirages at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a mirage, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! What's the deal with this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I can't help it,\Nyou damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's raise the sails! Undo the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay in the cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm going to stay\Nby Grandpa Ryu's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! There's nothing you\Ncan do by staying with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's feeling lonesome!\NI hafta hurry to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit down and shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We need to hurry back\Ndown and get out of danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like this sea's trying\Nto push the ship back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! This storm is no big deal at--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! No! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will save you! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised we'd go\Nto your nest together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lasso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! There's light over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the eye of the typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see an island below that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to land there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking him to\Nthe dragons' nest, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stormy seas surround the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like they're trying\Nto keep people away from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be why nobody's\Never found it before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems more like a castle\Nthat's sunk into the sea than an island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Check it out!\NDoesn't that seem shaped like a dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be where the\NMillennial Dragon lives after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Dragons sure are skillful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! It was obviously\Nhumans who made this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it to Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does anyone even live here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole place has been\Nswallowed up by Mother Nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where do you suppose\Nthe dragons' nest is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!\NI'm talking to you, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! We're at the dragon nest\Nisland now! Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says this might not be Lost Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went all the way through\Nthat stormy sea just to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the top there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could look down at the\Nwhole island from up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Trying to figure things\Nout here won't get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go have a look!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Nami makes\Nthe men do all the work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, "Try pushing it yourself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Less complaining\Nand more pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start getting cocky, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining and push!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Nami-san is so nice\Nwhen she's snappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a city...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Everything is broken everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did people really used to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, given all of these houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why's there no one here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe they found\Na better island to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennial Dragon's mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Millennial Dragon play\Nwith children here on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you guys friends\Nof the Millennial Dragon too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Apis. Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?!\NThese birds told me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said there's a building\Non the summit with a dragon mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it... I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for showing us the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've sure come up a long ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This painting is of the\NMillennial Dragon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This building is the dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Where's the entrance?\NHow do we get inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no handle\Nor keyhole anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you supposed to open it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! That pendant... You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually a key that opens\Nthe door to the dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're so little, Apis!\N--So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're alive... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what was that about it\Nbeing a key just a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case, we're inside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.75,0:22:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Is this really Lost Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Look at that! This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!\NHe followed us all the way here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's fight! You too, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Now there's a huge armada!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showdown in the Ruins!\NTense Zoro vs. Eric!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
